					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p187009">Re: Reset handler/reset vector confusion?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=187009&amp;sid=b7c0f896d3cd99914472825958f09c0d#p187009"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Wed Jan 18, 2017 12:54 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
